        <p> Content Inside Box</p>
        
    </div>

    <div class="box-description">
        <p>This Example demonstrates the CSS box model:</p>
        <p><strong> 1. Content:</strong> The white area int center where the text is displayed.</p>
        <p><strong> 2. Padding:</strong> The space between the content and the border (light gray).</p>
        <p><strong> 3. Border:</strong> The solid blue line surrounding the box.</p>
        <p><strong> 4. Margin:</strong> The space outside the border (moves the box away from other elements).</p>
    </div>

